@Host = http://localhost:5146
@PostId = 18fb9b2b-de50-4ef0-aabd-02ef843e7d98

### Create a New Post
POST {{Host}}/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "First Post",
  "content": "This is the initial content."
}

### Get Post by ID (Cache Miss/Hit)
GET {{Host}}/api/posts/{{PostId}}

### Update Post (Triggers Cache Eviction)
PUT {{Host}}/api/posts/{{PostId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Post Title",
  "content": "This content has been modified."
}

### Verify Cache Eviction (Should fetch fresh from DB)
GET {{Host}}/api/posts/{{PostId}}

### Test Validation (Unprocessable Entity)
POST {{Host}}/api/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "content": ""
}